<view class="page">
  <view class="section">
    <view class="title">我的资料</view>
    <view class="subtitle">MVP 暂时保存在本机，接入微信登录后会同步到服务端。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel" wx:if="{{profile}}">
    <view class="profile-row">
      <view class="label">大学</view>
      <view>{{profile.universityCode}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="profile-row">
      <view class="label">Programme</view>
      <view>{{profile.programmeName}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="profile-row">
      <view class="label">Major</view>
      <view>{{profile.majorName}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="profile-row">
      <view class="label">Curriculum Year</view>
      <view>{{profile.curriculumYear}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="profile-row">
      <view class="label">当前年级</view>
      <view>Year {{profile.currentYear}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel" wx:else>
    <view class="panel-title">还没有设置专业</view>
    <view class="subtitle">设置后可以查看匹配课程和毕业要求。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="button" bindtap="goOnboarding">{{profile ? '修改资料' : '开始设置'}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section vault">
    <view class="vault-mark">LOCAL VAULT</view>
    <view class="panel-title">数据保险箱</view>
    <view class="vault-copy">把资料、收藏、已修记录和 Study Plan 复制成一份文本备份。数据不会上传服务器。</view>
    <view class="vault-actions">
      <view class="vault-button primary" bindtap="copyBackup">复制备份</view>
      <view class="vault-button" bindtap="restoreBackup">从剪贴板恢复</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="panel-title">数据说明</view>
    <view class="subtitle">当前为 MVP 示例数据。正式上线前，每门课程都会展示官方来源链接和最后核验时间；毕业检查仅供参考，以大学官方要求为准。</view>
  </view>
</view>
